title: Bowl SZN
description:
Big Cat, Lightswitch Lou and Matt are joined in studio by the Pick Em Intern Champion Blackjack Fletcher. Blackjack breaks down his sequence-filled fit as well as the best matchups this week. The whole gang gives their picks for the college football games everyone is talking about and some picks flying under the radar this Bowl season!!!


You can find every episode of this show on Apple Podcasts, Spotify or YouTube. Prime Members can listen ad-free on Amazon Music. For more, visit barstool.link/barstoolpickem
